        <mxCell id="rp-ha-note" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f8cecc;strokeColor=#b85450;fontSize=11;fontStyle=0;align=left;" value="⚠  HA Rules — memorise these&#xa;&#xa;etcd quorum = 2 of 3 must be alive&#xa;1 node down  →  cluster continues normally&#xa;2 nodes down →  etcd halts · API unavailable&#xa;&#xa;Kube-VIP failover  ~1-2s  (ARP re-election)&#xa;Pod reschedule      ~40-60s (separate event)&#xa;These are INDEPENDENT — VIPs move fast,&#xa;pods move slow. Do not confuse them." vertex="1">
